Definition: a vacuum tube in which a hot cathode emits a beam of electrons that pass through a high voltage anode and are focused or deflected before hitting a phosphorescent screen
Synonyms: CRT, gas-discharge_tube, oscilloscope, p, television, computer, a, vacuum, tube, in, which, hot, cathode, emits, beam, of, electrons, that, pass, through, high, voltage, anode, and, are, focused, or, deflected, before, hitting, phosphorescent, screen
Category: noun.artifact
